latestPosts.caption:
@damienqd calls on all creators, artists, and producers! The iconic single “Listen To The Music” by Judy Carter, originally released in 1983 in collaboration with Paco Rabanne, has returned to streaming platforms fully remastered — and it’s ready to be remixed by you! Film it, tag it, #RabanneRemix it. ​

Discover how you could get the chance to be invited to co-produce a brand new track at @miravalstudios on rabanne.com. ​
_ ​
#RabanneRemix #Rabanne #RabanneTalents​

In the ‘80s, Paco Rabanne pioneered the fusion of fashion and music — championing Afro-disco, funk, and the sounds of a generation. Today, that legacy is reborn. In collaboration with @miravalstudios, Rabanne re-releases “Listen to the Music” by Judy Carter and invites a new wave of creators to remix the track.​

Enter the #RabanneRemix challenge for a chance to get invited to @miravalstudios and finalize your track. Download the track on rabanne.com, remix it, and post your unique vision of tomorrow’s sound on TikTok between 9 July and 31 August.​

Discover more on rabanne.com.​
_​
#RabanneRemix #Rabanne #RabanneTalents
